SUMMARY:Studio55: Photography
LOCATION:120 W Gasparilla Plaza Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:In this class\, students will explore a range of photographic 
 compositions using props and face paint to create one-of-a-kind\, temporar
 y settings\, captured as fine art photography. Working with still life\, s
 elf-portraits\, and close-up abstract images\, students will learn the bas
 ics of photography while drawing inspiration from the exhibition Avant Gar
 de: Remarkable Women in the Permanent Collection\, featuring artists such 
 as Salina Roman\, Wendy Babcox\, and Angela Kullman. Sundays\, Jun 7 - Jun
  28  1:004:00 PM (4 classes) Ages 55  Beginner-Intermediate Level This cla
 ss located at the Firehouse Cultural Center in Ruskin\, FL \n\nPermalink: 
 https://www.tampa.gov/node/188676
