SUMMARY:Fathers Day Experience at Rusty Pelican Tampa.
LOCATION:2425 N Rocky Point Dr= Tampa \, FL 33607 United States
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Dad by the water this Fathers Day at Rusty Pelican T
 ampa. Fathers Day at Rusty Pelican Tampa is a full experience. Whether you
 re joining us for brunch\, dinner\, or making it an all-day affair\, weve 
 got the bay views\, bold flavors\, and festive cocktails to make it one to
  remember. Three-Course Chefs Brunch  10:00 AM  4:00 PM  105 adults  35 ch
 ildren Start with a shareable appetizer and fresh coastal raw bar platter\
 , then move into plated favorites like Lobster Benedict\, Hot Honey Fried 
 Chicken Belgian Waffle\, Surf Turf\, and Grilled Lobster Tail. Close with 
 family-style desserts to share around the table. Toast Dad with the limite
 d-edition cocktail. The Walk This Way features a Milk-Clarified Bulleit Bo
 urbon cocktail with lime\, bitters\, and mint\, or sip on tableside Bloody
  Marys and mix-and-match bottomless mimosas in flavors like mango Tajn\, c
 ucumber mint\, watermelon lime\, and classic orange. (30 add-on per person
 ) Signature Dinner  5:00 PM  9:00 PM Already have daytime plans? End Fathe
 rs Day on a high note. The full dinner menu is available that evening  pri
 me cuts\, fresh seafood\, and handcrafted cocktails with a view. Dont miss
  The Steak Progressive (three premium cuts\, one legendary plate) and sign
 ature cocktails like The Finest Hour.  Sunday\, June 15\, 2026  2425 N Roc
 ky Point Dr\, Tampa\, FL Fathers Day on the water fills fast and Reservati
 ons are highly encouraged. Book your table today: https:bit.lyrptfathersda
 y (https:bit.lyrptfathersday) \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/19
 0991
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/190991
END:VEVENT
