SUMMARY:Stars\, Stripes Science
LOCATION:4801 E Fowler Ave Tampa \, FL 33617-2017 United States
DESCRIPTION:Are you ready for one of the most exciting 4th of July events 
 in Tampa? Celebrate Independence Day at MOSI with Stars\, Stripes\, Scienc
 e ! Enjoy live music\, planetarium shows (https:mosi.orgexperiencesaunders
 -planetarium)\, food drinks\, science demos\, and more! Guests can discove
 r crowd favorites like the rainbow fire demo\, liquid nitrogen ice cream\,
  baseball-themed activities\, games\, and even a dunk tank! In the Saunder
 s Planetarium (https:mosi.orgexperiencesaunders-planetarium)\, families ca
 n experience special presentations on the dome screen\, including a sensor
 y-friendly fireworks experience at 4:30 PM\, guided star tours\, and addit
 ional fireworks shows that are not designated sensory friendly. Best of al
 l\, your participation helps support MOSIs mission to inspire curiosity an
 d a love of science. What to Expect: Live Music by The Julie Black Duo (ht
 tps:www.julieblackmusic.com) Planetarium Shows (sensory-friendly show at 4
 :30PM) Liquid Nitrogen Ice Cream Baseball-themed Activities Science Demos 
 Carnival-style Games Food Drink Vendors Ticket Upgrades: Purchase an upgra
 ded ticket for 360 views of Tampas fireworks from the Dome Rooftop. Also\,
  enjoy select complimentary refreshments and exclusive telescope viewings 
 of the night sky. Guests are strongly encouraged to wear comfortable\, sen
 sible shoes for rooftop and telescope viewings. \n\nPermalink: https://www
 .tampa.gov/node/191566
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/191566
END:VEVENT
